Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveTwo soldiers, intending couple, have been killed on their way to their wedding in Imo.
The detail of the crime is not clear yet, but an audio revealing a phone conversation likely make “unknown gunmen’ the perpetrators.
In the phone conversation obtained by LIB, a man confessed to killing the couple—a master warrant officer and his juior female officer—and two others.
The killer came soldiers have been killing people, and he has “eaten these ones” in revenge.
A military source also told LIB that the couple were beheaded and their private parts were also mutilated.
